nt\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1699}, {\"ngram\": \"hostage negotiations\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1721}, {\"ngram\": \"clinical features\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"deployment\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1758}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual harassment\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"psychological first aid\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"financial management\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1824}, {\"ngram\": \"substance abuse\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once in the DRC, soldier will face up to ongoing fighting between rebel groups, including the ADF (Allied Democratic Forces) and M23 on one side with DRC President Felix Tshisekedi's FARDC (Forces Armees de la Republic Democratique du Congo) and \\\"their force\\\" - the tri-nation SAMIDRC (SADC Mission in the DRC) as those fighting for peace and security.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 2200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1860, \"end\": 1863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Democratic_Republic_of_the_Congo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.957540836709573e-29, \"text\": \"DRC\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Democratic_Republic_of_the_Congo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Democratic_Republic_of_the_Congo\"}, {\"begin\": 1942, \"end\": 1945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allied_Democratic_Forces\", \"score\": 0.9988730684726139, \"rank\": 0.0011282029347355717, \"text\": \"ADF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allied_Democratic_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allied_Democratic_Forces\"}, {\"begin\": 1947, \"end\": 1971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allied_Democratic_Forces\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Allied Democratic Forces\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allied_Democratic_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allied_Democratic_Forces\"}, {\"begin\": 1977, \"end\": 1980, \"title\":